==English==

===Etymology===
Compare French ''[[achromatisme]]''

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# The state or quality of being [[achromatic]]; as, the '''achromatism''' of a lens; [[achromaticity]].
# The state of being free of [[color]]s, not [[emit]]ting or [[separate|separating]] into colors.
# [[achromatopia|Achromatopia]].

